mod_spox
    http://modspox.rubyforge.org
    Author: spox
    
== Description

A Ruby IRC bot

== Usage

Configuration:

mod_spox --config

Running:

mod_spox

== Requirements

 * fastthread
 * sequel
 * termios
 
== Install

gem install --include-dependencies mod_spox

